        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Arctic Refuge Protection Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill designates approximately 1,559,538 acres of land within Alaska in the Arctic National Wildlife Refuge as a component of the National Wilderness Preservation System.</p>]]>
        </text>
